  DEFINE_AUTH_ROUTE(wrapper, impl) macro — generates a RouteHandler that checks the session cookie, returns 401 immediately if invalid, otherwise
  calls fork_and_run with the inner handler and authenticated username.

  /whoami — demonstration authenticated endpoint. The child calls getuid()/getgid()/getcwd() and returns them in JSON, proving it's running as the
  actual OS user with their home as CWD.


